OL,3,CCouncils and mayors urge government to
OL,4,Cgive them power to block betting shops
OL,6,FMore than 30 local authorities have
OL,7,Fraised concerns about the growing
OL,8,Fnumber of so-called "24-hour slot
OL,9,Fshops" on high streets, as ITV News
OL,10,FPolitical Correspondent Shehab Khan
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThis article contains mentions of
OL,14,Fsuicide and gambling addiction
OL,16,FCouncils and mayors from across the UK
OL,17,Fhave written to the government calling
OL,18,Ffor urgent reform of gambling laws,
OL,19,Fciting concerns over the number of
OL,20,Fslot machine and betting shops opening
OL,21,Fon high streets.
