OL,3,CCouncils and mayors urge government to
OL,4,Cgive them power to block betting shops
OL,6,FIn a letter seen exclusively by ITV
OL,7,FNews, 36 councils and two mayors,
OL,8,Frepresenting more than 12 million
OL,9,Fpeople, describe current gambling laws
OL,10,Fas "desperately out of date" and urge
OL,11,Fgovernment action.
OL,13,FLed by Brent Council - and supported
OL,14,Fby high profile names like Andy
OL,15,FBurnham, Mayor of Greater Manchester -
OL,16,Fthe letter highlights the growing
OL,17,Fpresence of gambling operators and
OL,18,Fincreased gambling-related harm.
