OL,6,F"We're not against gambling or
OL,7,Fgambling establishments," Patel told
OL,8,Fme. "We've just had a load of
OL,9,Fconcentration of them, that is the
OL,10,Fproblem."
OL,12,FShe accused gambling companies of
OL,13,Fintentionally setting up more shops
OL,14,Fareas with higher levels of
OL,15,Fdeprivation like Brent.
OL,17,F"At the moment Harlesden's average
OL,18,Fincome is under #24,000 a year, which
OL,19,Fis well below the London average... so
OL,20,Fit's strategically targeting
OL,21,Fvulnerable people," she said.
