OL,3,CCouncils and mayors urge government to
OL,4,Cgive them power to block betting shops
OL,6,FThe rise of slot machines,
OL,7,Fparticularly B3 gaming machines, has
OL,8,Fbeen a focal point of concern.
OL,10,FThese machines, commonly found in
OL,11,Fcasinos, betting shops, bingo halls,
OL,12,Fand adult gaming centres, allow a
OL,13,Fmaximum stake of #2 with a maximum
OL,14,Fprize of #500.
OL,16,FSince the pandemic, the number of
OL,17,Fgambling machines has surged,
OL,18,Fincreasing from around 171,000 to
OL,19,F202,000.
