OL,6,FFor some individuals, these machines
OL,7,Fact as a gateway to more addictive
OL,8,Fforms of gambling. Sean Alexander, who
OL,9,Fbegan using slot machines, later
OL,10,Fbecame addicted and then transitioned
OL,11,Fto online gambling, where he lost
OL,12,F#50,000 in just a few months.
OL,14,F"I could be on the fruit machine for
OL,15,Fthree, four hours... I was stuck on
OL,16,Fthe machine just chasing this high of
OL,17,Fwinning the jackpot," he told me.
