OL,3,CCouncils and mayors urge government to
OL,4,Cgive them power to block betting shops
OL,6,F"I was suicidally depressed by the end
OL,7,Fof it," Sean said. "As a man of 30
OL,8,Fyears old, I had had a house and
OL,9,Feverything, on paper I had it all, but
OL,10,Fthere was a deep unhappiness that
OL,11,Fmeant I was looking for quick fixes
OL,12,Fthrough gambling."
OL,14,F"It took everything, it took away my
OL,15,Fjob, my girlfriend at the time,
OL,16,Ffriends."
OL,18,FExperts believe the rise in the number
OL,19,Fof machines is partly due to increased
OL,20,Frevenue per machine.
