OL,6,FWill Prochaska, a gambling campaigner,
OL,7,Fwarned of the dangers of the machines:
OL,9,F"We're sometimes seeing people who are
OL,10,Ftrying to recover from a gambling
OL,11,Faddiction online and they may have
OL,12,Fself-excluded from online forms of
OL,13,Fgambling, but they're lured in by the
OL,14,Fshops on the high street," he said.
OL,16,F"So they're actually targeting
OL,17,Faddicts, this is really dangerous
OL,18,Fstuff that we're talking about."
