OL,6,FUrging the government to take action
OL,7,Fon the letter from the councils and
OL,8,Fmayors, he added: "All of the council
OL,9,Fservices that are stretched - things
OL,10,Flike homelessness services, the
OL,11,Fpolice, and mental health services -
OL,12,Fare now having to pick up the pieces
OL,13,Fof this industry making profit from
OL,14,Ftheir residents."
OL,16,FIn response to ITV News' story, the
OL,17,FGambling Commission stated that all
OL,18,Fgambling businesses are required to
OL,19,Fact if they observe signs of gambling
OL,20,Fharm and said they were "tough on
OL,21,Foperators who fail to do this".
