OL,6,FThe British Gaming Council represents
OL,7,Fcasinos and betting shops. Betting
OL,8,Fshops are restricted to four machines
OL,9,Fper venue, by law.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Betting and
OL,12,FGaming Council, said: "BGC members
OL,13,Fhold the highest standards on age
OL,14,Fverification and safer gambling
OL,15,Fstandards.
OL,17,F"Each month around 22.5 million people
OL,18,Fin Britain enjoy a bet while most
OL,19,Frecent NHS Health Survey for England
OL,20,Festimated that 0.4 per cent of the
OL,21,Fadult population are problem gamblers."
